Menlyn Boutique Hotel offers business travellers a dependable base in Menlyn. Every room includes a proper work surface, quality linen and blackout curtains, and the property has been assessed against the Acosa Business Traveller Essentials framework.

## The property

Guests consistently highlight the reliable connectivity, straightforward check-in after long travel days, and staff who understand that a corporate stay runs on a different rhythm to a holiday.

## Getting around

The property is positioned for quick access to the node's main office precincts, with secure on-site parking and simple routes to the highway.
